with this -- whether
it's latent or another form of
sexism that

41:37.862 --> 41:39.497 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
may be going on?

41:39.530 --> 41:41.933 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RICHARD TRUMKA, President,
AFL-CIO: Well,
I think he's successfully tapped
into the

41:41.966 --> 41:47.338 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
