enough against
what's almost a siren song
coming from Donald

43:49.126 --> 43:53.331 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Trump that, I will be there for
you, this
is a -- we live in a fearful
time, it's a

43:53.364 --> 43:59.437 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
