need somebody
to protect us, and I will be
there and I will

43:59.470 --> 44:02.173 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
create jobs and build a wall,
and I will do
all the rest of it?

44:02.206 --> 44:07.211 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RICHARD TRUMKA: Judy, you forget
that we face
a campaign of fear and division
every day

44:07.245 --> 44:11.115 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
