from Donald Trump.

46:04.195 --> 46:05.997 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

46:06.030 --> 46:07.832 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CORY BOOKER: Well, speaking as
somebody who
