grow, I have
to say I like a person like
Hillary Clinton

46:16.474 --> 46:18.209 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
who is willing to analyze the
facts.

46:18.242 --> 46:20.878 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
