46:53.678 --> 46:58.349 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So the things that have built
this country,
strong middle-class jobs, we're
fighting for

46:58.382 --> 47:00.284 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
