that I heard
around my kitchen table about
what she experienced.

48:30.975 --> 48:32.743 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
So, I know we have a lot.

48:32.777 --> 48:37.481 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But I do know that this history
we're making
tonight, when Hillary Clinton
will accept

48:37.515 --> 48:42.119 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the nomination, I think it's
going to go good
steps in helping this country
heal from its

48:42.153 --> 48:46.924 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
