and that discrimination
has no place in politics, in the
workplace

48:51.829 --> 48:53.631 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
or anywhere at all.

48:53.664 --> 48:57.701 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Rich Trumka,
let's just come
back to that first question we
talked about,

48:57.735 --> 49:00.838 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
