49:00.871 --> 49:06.477 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Are you having, are your
associates having
honest conversations, as Senator
Booker just

49:06.510 --> 49:10.214 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
