50:28.425 --> 50:32.429 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Our country really is coming to
a point where
we're having more constructive
conversations.

50:32.463 --> 50:33.430 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And I have tremendous hope.

50:33.464 --> 50:34.431 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
RICHARD TRUMKA: Yes.

50:34.465 --> 50:36.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Yes, I think so too.

50:36.333 --> 50:36.834 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: And it's a
conversation we're
going to have to continue
another time, because

50:36.867 --> 50:38.002 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
