51:32.189 --> 51:33.991 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, that's a great conversations
starter.

51:34.024 --> 51:35.793 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
My name is Jon Grinspan.

51:35.826 --> 51:39.530 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I'm a curator at the National
Museum of American
History.

51:39.563 --> 51:41.365 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It's a lot of being nice to
people.

51:41.398 --> 51:44.535 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
